6
0:00:27.293,000 --> 0:00:31,000
I mean, this is the super ultimate "why" question?

7
0:00:31.939,000 --> 0:00:33,000
So I'm going to talk about the mystery of existence,

8
0:00:34.174,000 --> 0:00:35,000
the puzzle of existence,

9
0:00:35.73,000 --> 0:00:37,000
where we are now in addressing it,

10
0:00:38.644,000 --> 0:00:4,000
and why you should care,

11
0:00:40.894,000 --> 0:00:41,000
and I hope you do care.

12
0:00:42.81,000 --> 0:00:44,000
