26
0:01:17.718,000 --> 0:01:19,000
"It is not how things are in the world

27
0:01:20.408,000 --> 0:01:21,000
that is the mystical,

28
0:01:21.76,000 --> 0:01:23,000
it's that the world exists."

29
0:01:24.095,000 --> 0:01:26,000
And if you don't like taking your epigrams

30
0:01:26.313,000 --> 0:01:28,000
